Package Application.Exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DumpCreationException
    Exception thrown when trying to obtain the data dump for a Scenario
    GetCanonicalPathException
    Exception thrown by Application when trying to register locations for Application.IMAGE_DIR, Application.IMAGE_SCEN_DIR, Application.LOG_DIR, Application.PROF_DIR or Application.ACH_DIR.
    JarAccessException
    Exception thrown by LanguageFilesUtils when trying to access files of the deployed and running jar.
    NoQuizFoundException
    Exception thrown by DeletedScenarioManagementController and ScenarioManagementController when viewing information for a Scenario for which a Quiz is not present.
    PictureCreationException
    Exception thrown by ImageProcessor, VisionController and VisionManagementController when trying to create an image.
    PictureUploadException
    Exception thrown by ProfileController and ScenarioManagementController when trying to upload an image for a User's profile or for a Scenario.
    TranslateException
    Exception thrown by TranslationUtil, UnsplashConnector, VisionController and VisionManagementController when trying to translate a search term from a given language to English for Unsplash.
    UnsplashConnectionException
    Exception thrown by UnsplashConnector, VisionController, and VisionManagementController when trying to access Unsplash's API for retrieving photos to use in visions.
